---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumb from "../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions"
  description="Terms and Conditions for Ashaz Autoz."
>
  <div class="pt-24">
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <Breadcrumb path="/terms/" class="mb-8" />
        <article class="max-w-3xl prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert">
          <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
          <p class="text-muted">Last updated: January 1, 2024</p>

          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing and using the Ashaz Autoz website, you agree to comply with and be bound by these terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website or services.</p>

          <h2>2. Services</h2>
          <p>Ashaz Autoz provides vehicle sales, vehicle import services, car rentals, workshop and maintenance services, and related automotive services in Timor-Leste. All services are subject to availability and specific terms agreed upon at the time of service.</p>

          <h2>3. Vehicle Listings</h2>
          <p>Vehicle listings on our website are for informational and showcase purposes only. Prices, specifications, and availability are subject to change without prior notice. We make every effort to ensure accuracy but cannot guarantee that all information is complete or current.</p>

          <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>All content on this website, including text, images, logos, and designs, is the property of Ashaz Autoz and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. Unauthorized use is prohibited.</p>

          <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Ashaz Autoz shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our website or services.</p>

          <h2>6. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Timor-Leste.</p>

          <h2>7. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website.</p>

          <h2>8. Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these terms, please contact us at our yard in Ponte Foun, Comoro, Dili, Timor-Leste or call 7715 4379.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
